---
title: Steakhouse-Style Salmon with a Creamy Pan Sauce, Roasted Potatoes & Lemony Broccoli
description: Our chefs gave pork chops a steak-like treatment, transforming the everyday protein into something extraordinary. Tender chops are coated in a bold and savory steak spice, seared, then drizzled with a creamy pan sauce. And like any great steakhouse-style meal, the sides are just as impressive. Roasted potatoes and lemony broccoli round everything out. Now all you need is someone to bring you a dessert menu!
